::sighs:: i know i havent updated for awhile ...been so busy ...im home this weekend unfortunately ...i was supposed to go camping but i got sick on wed/ thurs and am still really congested...i have to say i miss my friends...everyone else is so busy too...like no one has time anymore ... sighs ...sometimes i feel closer to the people at work and the kids i sit then my own friends ...that makes me so sad ... crystal refuses to call anyone ...she thinks if she calls no one, no one will call her ...with the exception of me and occasionally sam thats pretty much the way it is... john tells me im dumb for thinking of calling anyone i havent talked to in awhile ...yeah i mean i guess they probably dont care too much but you sometimes people are just to busy ...sigh...im really looking forward to my friend stephy coming to visit...i miss the days at ku with her and i really dont want to loose touch with her...i also cant wait to go visit her ...just a trip away would be good ...im really hopin my cousin manda comes in too this summer but its a long shot ...sighs...back to friends ...i dunno why i have such a hard time letting go of them ...even if i know they dont care  ...i just let people walk all over me ...but then i feel bad if i dont ...::shrugs:: i cant win but i think im gonna try to stick to crystals plan with a few exceptions... i just wanna have fun and be happy instead of worrying about who really gives a damn and who doesnt ..although i have to say with the exception of not spending much time with my friends ..i have been having a pretty good summer ...ive been spending time with my lil sister and my lil cousins (always exciting) and as much time as i can with johnny ...no matter what im upset about just seeing him just seems to make me happy (we just passed our year and a half mark :^) and everything has been really smooth for awhile!!!)

in other news i have 3 turtles ...not that you care ...but i love them to pieces ...they are so amusing to watch ...they make me smile too...oh and i have a really big inflatable turtle in our pool ...oh yeah and an alligator, a croc, and a killer whale (oh a penguin tube too) ..yeah its a zoo but my sister, brother and i have a blast ..another thing that totally makes this summer rock !! this is the first year our pool is open all summer last year it was open for like august but this year totally ownes all. but anyway im rambling and i think im gonna get in the shower!!!!

<FONT color=#ff6666>So yeah I am finally done with school...well for the summer... i was thinking about taking summer courses but nah im good ..ill probably end up working a shit load this summer anyway ...i actually kinda like my new job ...i dont like some people there but i just laugh at them ...So anyway Friday ...the physics final...i found out nothing sucks more then thinking you are going into a 2 hr final and finding out its a 4 hr final ...especially since i was suppose to have lunch with my dad bc he was gonna help me pick out a digital camera...but oh well ...im gonna go do that today when im done with this...but yeah i decided that i didnt get all A's this semester which sucks because this is the closest i have ever gotten ...i ran into my philosophy teacher on Friday and he told me he gave me a B+ and asked me if that was cool ...i said thats good ..i really wanted to punch him in the face though ...not like its his fault but his grades are wacked ...like a 92 is an A and then below to and 82 is a B ...its messed up ..yeah ...anyway im getting really excited to go to SOUTH CAROLINA ...with my homies!! we leave sunday it is so gonna rock...also thrusday is my BIRTHDAY!!!! that makes me happy ...i am going to be 20 ...one more year baby til 21 !!!!!of course my best friend and my boyfriend turn 21 in october ...not to mention my cousin manda turns 21 next month to bad shes in illinois but hopefully ill get to see her this summer its been awhile...but anyways thats it for now ...oh and by the way i have a xanga now too ...just so you all know i was bored last night so i decided to make one of those too...since more people i know have them anyway ...but dont worry livejournal is still my number one!!!</FONT>

Yeah so I just had a mentally exhausting day. I had my trig final and my essay history final. I think I did well. Well we shall see. I believe I had straight A's going into the finals but some of them were borderline so fingers crossed. Last night I typed a 4 page paper in an hour ...I am still proud of myself for that one and that 10 page paper i did in 6 hours the night before it was due (this was including research too) I got an A on so i am very proud of myself. Yeah but anyway I can not wait for school to be over. I only have one more final so its sooooo close to being over.

My birthday is in one week! and I am going to Myrtle beach next weekend!!!!!!!!!!!!! BOOOOYA!!

Lets see what have I been up too...well planning my pool party ...i havent set a date yet but it should be fun stephy is gonna come to visit and we are gonna dorney park it ...i want to ride the new coaster hydra so bad ...i did the virtual ride online its pretty cool...a couple weekends ago now i went to the movies with beckie...we saw amityville horror...it wasnt scary but it was pretty good...then me her and blb went to dennys ...i havent been there in awhile and i hadnt hung out with davey for quite sometime so it was cool ...crystal is away now on her internship...i miss her soooo much ...i need my nightly phone convo for hours...i talked to marguerite, erin, and justin the other week or two..that was cool i decided to try to regain touch with some of the friends i havent talked to in awhile...::sigh:: i cant wait for summer...im hopin to chill alot with my beckie and spend sometime with my lil cousins...i am definitly gonna give the pool a work out too...i decided against working fultime i figure i have plenty of time for that when i get out of school besides to me right now money is not really an issue.

Anyway i am rambling on and on again so i am gonna go call my baby and bother him since crystal seems to not be picking up her phone!!!

This was an awesome weekend! I went camping with my bestest friends crystal and beckie and crystals mommy and daddy up at hickory run. The weather was awesome but due to some smoker guy we couldnt have fires because he started a forrest fire. People were still allowed to smoke though. so not fair...but we still had fun we went all the way accross the boulder field...and back...i climbed down inside this huge hole in the middle of the field...we played bull pit and cowpies..we made a lil twig fire in a tiny habachi grill since we wernt allowed to have a big one ..it was so cool ...then on sunday we decided to go hiking through the rhodadendron and i found the coolest water fall. so all and all a wonderful weekend. Unfortunately i some how ended up with pink eye ..now in both eyes ...i couldnt even open my right eye yesterday ...but i got to miss school with a doctors note which is always the best because they cant give you any shit.

So yeah im sittin here trying to write this ten page paper due for my history class on tuesday...which i might add  i havent really started but i just found out it was due tuesday on thursday and since i worked 9 hours friday and then again on Saturday and the fact that i procrastinate alot probably doesnt help much either but oh well ...but any way i cant think because i just had this arguement sort of with my dad about george bush ...lets just say im not in his favor or even close...but the my mom told me that growing up and even now they thought i had O.D.D...oppositional defiance disorder...which i have to say i was far from the perfect child growing up ...i was very stubborn and always argued and talked back ...i always had to have the last word....i was one of those kids that you could threaten with grounding them if they say another word and i would be grounded for a year before i shut up...once my friends got old enough to drive i just left ...if they said no i went out if they said be home by this time i would show up an hour later ...that kinda stuff...people with odd tend to grow out of it and do really well for themselves which is cool...i dont think i am quite out of it yet but like i know im not as bad as i use to be...anyway just thought i would blurb a bit ...

work...work sucks...i like my job but i am so bored have the time and there is so much drama there well i work with a shit load of girls...i like most of them though ...most of them are nice to me ...some arent but i just try to be nice to everyone because i really dont want to get involved in the drama...i wish i was 21 so i could go out drinkin with them after work ...it sucks because im like the only on under 21 but yeah anyway its going pretty well

i think im gonna go back to work now either that or im gonna call crystal ...i just cant seem to focas....uhhhh what a night...........

Today has been quite the day and normally i dont write about my kinda down times but i just feel like blowing off some steam. Last night i slept over at crystals which was cool we had fun and an ice cream binge... yummy yummy...today was kinda a downer for me ...i have just been so stressed out lately and thinking about a lot of stuff...i swear i wasnt even on the planet today...i hate the feeling when you want to help someone so bad but you have no clue what to do you are just helpless...another thing i kept thinking about was death bc i think my old dog is going to die soon which makes me very sad bc i love her very much ...then i start thinking about john dying or my friends, or my parents, or siblings...honestly i cant take it ...it like destroys me to think about it...but back to school ...i did so many stupid things today its kinda funny ...i walked into a bench on the way into class...i almost fell out of my desk during trig...i overflowed my cup in the caf bc i was staring off in to space at the bagels...i couldnt sit still just couldnt so me and beckie went outside then back in then out again ...we sat there visualizing the ocean because with the wind it was pacifing...this one kid jason called my name like 5 before i actually heard him ...then it took me a couple minutes just to realize who he was...i dont remember i thing we went over in class today...like i swear it must have been hilarious to watch me because i was totally out of it ...my history teacher called on me for something about what do you think stalin was thinkin ...i was just like he was probably pretty cheesed off...unfortunately the teacher wanted a more indept answer...lol...yesterday i played hackysack for a bit it was fun ...i was hopin to do it again today but the people left before i got out there...its a good stress reliever.........so then later i came home and i went to johns house and i heard the funniest story of how he got duped...lol...he has this stalker girl at work bc all the girls at work want him ...he is a hot comodity ...but she was like do you wanna go for a ride with me and this guy (who was johns friend) ...and so he was like sure...so they go out and get in her car and are waiting for this dude...and then she is like oh i guess hes not coming and floors it out of the parking lot not even giving john a chance to say anything...apparently she is the worst driver in the world and he was scared shittless...but its an hilarious story ...i love john ...he always makes me feel better ...he tries so hard to be such a good boyfriend to me and i totally love him for that ...not many guys will go the extra mile for their girl...his cousins were at his house ..they are a lively bunch ..i love them though never a dull moment...it was his grammys birthday so we had cake and stuff...it was cool...sometimes everything just feels better when im in his arms...

in other news its like midnight and i cant sleep im just not tired i dont know why...i talked to stephy the other day and shes not taking the big house she found...i hate when people want the money up front ...but its cool ..i figure save your money and maybe we can pull something together for second semester...i miss my stephy...im really happy to have beckie and crystal though the good times never stop! who knows maybe the 4 of us in a place next year ...that would so totally rock! but its been a long day i think im gonna try to go to sleep now ...or like benadryl it ...night night !!!!!
